              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">Youth Justice Board for England and Wales</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">YJB</xref>) is a non-departmental public body created to oversee the youth justice system for England and Wales.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">Youth Justice Board</xref>, see the gov.uk website at: 
